data.title: Fun and Run
data.text: This place was really cool. Kind of sporty with good food. We stopped in after moving my son into his college dorm. We were looking for something quick but yet fun to lift my mood😩 There were several big screen televisions which was awesome to watch the olympics. The was a great selection of food on the menu and the prices are reasonable. The staff is friendly and quick. That pretty much sums it up. Fun and Run. Enjoy!

data.title: Not want I expeced from a Strip Mall Reastaurant
data.text:
I went there with a business friend and we had a really good time. He kept ordering
appetizers and I thought we would never be able to eat our meals. But everything was so good, I thought we were going to explode before we left.
